huttle-mission%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%2520April%252014%252C%25201981%252C%2520the%2Cof%2520more%2520than%2520two%2520days.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20historic%20mission%20%26quot%3Bmarked%20the%20first%20NASA%20flight%20to%20end%20with%20a%20wheeled%20landing%20and%20represented%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20age%20of%20spaceflight%20that%20would%20employ%20the%20same%20hardware%20repeatedly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20300%2C000%20people%20showed%20up%20to%20see%20the%20groundbreaking%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20announcing%20the%20delivery%2C%20Joby%20has%20hit%20another%20significant%20milestone%20on%20its%20road%20to%20certification%20%E2%80%94%20piloted%20test%20flights.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Air%20Force%20personnel%20with%20Joby's%20experimental%20eVTOL.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c7a16617692f0d03e5649%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20personnel%20with%20Joby's%20experimental%20eVTOL.%3Cp%3EJoby%20Aviation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Joby%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20eVTOL%20test%20flights%20have%20been%20remotely%20piloted%20from%20a%20ground%20station%20%26quot%3Busing%20state-of-the-art%20communications%20technology%20and%20software.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20is%20finally%20putting%20a%20pilot%20in%20the%20cockpit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20four%20pilots%20have%20flown%20its%20electric%20pre-production%20prototype%20aircraft%2C%20who%20completed%20%26quot%3Ba%20series%20of%20initial%20tests%20that%20included%20free%20thrustborne%20hovers%20and%20forward%20transitions%20to%20semi-thrustborne%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20flights%2C%20which%20were%20performed%20at%20Joby's%20productio