4f9f2c156f5190019fd07c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222073%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20often%20canceled%20on%20meetings%2C%20according%20to%20his%20biographer.%3Cp%3EEduardo%20Munoz%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20supposed%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20WEF's%20flagship%20event%20in%20Davos.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20he%20decided%20not%20to%20show%20up%20the%20night%20before%20the%20event%2C%20per%20Michael%20Lewis'%20biography%20on%20the%20disgraced%20FTX%20founder.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELewis%20wrote%20SBF%20would%20cancel%20on%20people%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20he'd%20done%20some%20math%20in%20his%20head%20that%20proved%20that%20you%20weren't%20worth%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20supposed%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum's%20annual%20meeting%20in%20Davos%20%E2%80%94%20but%20decided%20to%20pull%20out%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20according%20to%20Michael%20Lewis'%20biography%20on%20the%20former%20FTX%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbcevents.com%2Fwef2022%2F%23%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbcevents.com%2Fwef2022%2F%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eonline%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20showed%20Bankman-Fried%20listed%20as%20a%20speaker%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Davos.%20A%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20on%20Thursday%20this%20was%20an%20event%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20official%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELewis%20described%20Bankman-Fried's%20messy%20and%20chaotic%20schedule%20%E2%80%93%20which%20often%20changed%20because%20he%20would%20decide%20not%20to%20show%20up%20for%20meetings%20he%20had%20agreed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCEOs%20had%20flown%20to%20the%20Bahamas%20under%20the%20mistaken%20impressi