%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DilJd1mA8AHk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20episode%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BBloomberg%20Wealth%20with%20David%20Rubenstein.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHere%20are%20Marks'%208%20best%20quotes%2C%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E1.%20%26quot%3BWe%20never%20know%20where%20we're%20going%2C%20but%20we%20sure%20as%20hell%20ought%20to%20know%20where%20we%20are.%26quot%3B%20(Marks%20said%20he%20avoids%20making%20forecasts%2C%20but%20he%20believes%20that%20analyzing%20the%20market%20today%20is%20helpful%20in%20preparing%20for%20what%20the%20future%20holds.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2.%20%26quot%3BI%20agree%20with%20John%20Kenneth%20Galbraith%2C%20who%20said%20there%20are%20two%20kinds%20of%20forecasters%3A%20the%20ones%20who%20don't%20know%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20who%20don't%20know%20they%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20live%20on%20a%20shot%20of%20adrenaline%20every%20day%20for%2013%20years.%26quot%3B%20(Marks%20slammed%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20policy%20of%20near-zero%20interest%20rates%20between%202009%20and%202021%2C%20saying%20it%20subsidized%20borrowing%20and%20punished%20lending%20and%20saving.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20through%20a%20period%20when%20it's%20super%20easy%20to%20raise%20money%20for%20any%20purpose%20or%20no%20purpose%2C%20and%20you%20go%20into%20a%20period%20when%20it's%20difficult%20to%20raise%20money%20even%20for%20a%20good%20purpose%2C%20clearly%20many%20more%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20founder.%26quot%3B%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foleary-regional-banks-commercial-real-estate-small-business-rates-lending-2023-9%5C%22%3ESeveral%20experts%20have%20warned%3C%2Fa%3E%20steeper%20borrowing%20costs%20will%20lead%20to%20more%20loan%20defaults%2C%20pressure%20on%20asset%20prices%2C%20and%20tighter%20lending%20standards%20that%20will%20hammer%20the%20likes%20of%20small%20businesses%20and%20commercial%20real%20estate%20developers.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20clearly%20worrisome.%20There's%20never%20been%20a%20bankruptcy%20of%20the%20US%20or%20a%20country%20like%20it%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20know%20what's%20going%20to%20happen.%20This%20business%20about%20using%20a%20default%20as%20a%20negotiating%20tool%20is%20very%2C%20very%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%20(Marks%20was%20bemoaning%20the%20political%20skirmishes%20over%20raising%20the%20debt%20ceiling%20earlier%20this%20year.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20golden%20goose.%20We%20have%20this%20reserve%20currency%20status%20because%20the%20dollar%20is%20the%20safest%20currency%20in%20the%20world%20and%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20the%20best.%20Why%20would%20you%20jeopardize%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%26quot%3BWarren%20Buffett%20always%20talks%20about%20Ted%20Williams%20who%20batted%20.400.%20That%20means%2060%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20he%20was%20out%20at%20the%20plate.%20The%20great%20investors%20are%20right%2060%25%2C%2070%25%2C%20maybe%2080%25%20of%20the%20time.%20If%20you're%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20has%20to%20be%20right%20all%20the%20time%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20in%20investing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E8.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20markets%20are%20doing%20well%2C%20or%20when%20we're%20doing%20well%2C%20then%20people%20have%20that%20cocktail%20party%20conversation.%20When%20the%20markets%20are%20doing%20poorly%2C%20I%20just%20stand%20in%20the%20corner.%26quot%3B%20(Marks%20was%20joking%20that%20nobody%20asks%20him%20for%20investment%20advice%20in%20a%20depressed%20market.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoward-marks-us-dollar-loan-defaults-debt-ceiling-interest-rates-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696495639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651d8717617692f0d03ee488%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhoward-marks-us-dollar-loan-defaults-debt-ceiling-interest-rates-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Howard%20Marks%20cautioned%20against%20trying%20to%20predict%20the%20market%2C%20noted%20every%20investor%20makes%20mistakes%2C%20and%20joked%20about%20his%20popularity%20at%20cocktail%20parties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhoward-marks-us-dollar-loan-defaults-debt-ceiling-interest-rates-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%20May%20Add%20Rs%2022%2C000%20Crore%20To%20Indian%20Economy%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20may%20boost%20host%20country%20India's%20economy%20by%20as%20much%20as%20Rs%2022%2C000%20crore%20(%242.6%20billion)%2C%20economists%20at%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20quadrennial%20tournament%2C%20which%20starts%20on%20Thursday%20and%20runs%20through%20mid-November%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20draw%20large%20numbers%20of%20visiting%20fans%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%20With%20the%20matches%20played%20across%2010%20cities%2C%20that%20will%20mostly%20benefit%20the%20travel%20as%20well%20as%20hospitality%20sectors%2C%20wrote%20economists%20Jahnavi%20Prabhakar%20and%20Aditi%20Gupta%20in%20a%20note%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%2C%20which%20is%20being%20hosted%20in%20India%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202011%2C%20also%20coincides%20with%20the%20three-month%20festive%20season%20that%20started%20in%20September%20and%20will%20be%20particularly%20beneficial%20for%20the%20retail%20sector%20as%20many%20people%20will%20make%20%26quot%3Bsentimental%20purchases%20of%20merchandise%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20economists%20expec