rred%20critical%20cases%2C%20many%20of%20them%20newborns%2C%20to%20the%20government%20hospital%20and%20this%20pushed%20up%20the%20death%20count%20at%20the%20Nanded%20facility%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20set%20to%20tell%20the%20court.%20Private%20healthcare%20units%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20at%20least%2010%20newborns%20that%20were%20reported%20at%20the%20Nanded%20hospital%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20say%20in%20its%20affidavit%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fn0qrc608_nanded-hospital-gate-pti_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20on%20how%20the%20state%20government%20plans%20to%20respond%20in%20court%2C%20Medical%20Education%20minister%20Hasan%20Mashrif%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTen%20of%20the%20newborns%20who%20died%20had%20been%20brought%20(to%20the%20state-run%20hospital)%20from%20private%20hospitals.%20And%20they%20were%20in%20a%20very%20serious%20condition%20when%20they%20were%20brought%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20formed%20a%20committee%20and%20has%20conducted%20an%20audit%20of%20each%20death.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20put%20these%20all%20matters%20before%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%20has%20maintained%20that%20there%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20or%20doctors%20at%20the%20Nanded%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGround%20reports%20have%2C%20however%2C%20shown%20a%20different%20picture.%20NDTV%20found%20pigs%20roaming%20on%20the%20hospital%20premises%20and%20drains%20clogged%20by%20plastic%20bottles.%20Relatives%20of%20patients%20who%20had%20died%20at%20the%20hospital%20said%20they%20had%20to%20buy%20medicines%20from%20outside%20and%20no%20senior%20doctor%20was%20attending%20to%20the%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fik034kmg_pigs-roam-in-nanded-hospital_625x300_04_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dean%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20another%20doctor%20have%20been%20charged%20in%20a%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20after%20the%20newborn's%20relative%20alleged%20that%20the%20baby%20died%20due%20to%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20SR%20Wakode%2C%20the%20acting%20dean%2C%20had%20earlier%20registered%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Hemant%20Patil%20who%20made%20him%20clean%20a%20filthy%20toilet%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EViral%20videos%20showed%20Mr%20Patil%20asking%20the%20dean%20to%20clean%20the%20toilet.%20The%20Nanded%20MP%20has%20now%20been%20charged%20with%20IPC%20provisions%20relating%20to%20criminal%20force%20to%20deter%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20doing%20his%20duty%2C%20defamation%20and%20criminal%20intimidation.%20The%20MP%20was%20also%20charged%20under%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696495320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0gumjs4_nanded-hospital_625x300_02_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-to-blame-long-weekend-in-private-hospitals-for-nanded-deaths-sources-4452154%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Confronting%20a%20huge%20backlash%20over%2031%20deaths%20in%2072%20hours%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Nanded%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20is%20set%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20to%20private%20healthcare%20units%20in%20the%20area%20that%20were%20shut%20fo