%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03154731%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-154153_002-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03154731%2Fsignal-2023-10-03-154153_002-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678046%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScene%20at%20the%20Special%20Cell%20HQ%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20in%20Lodhi%20Colony.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20journalist%20called%20Rajeev%20Sharma%20was%20dramatically%20%E2%80%9Ccaptured%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20police%20in%20the%20car%20park%20of%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20faced%20hell%20for%20a%20long%20time%20until%20the%20courts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frajeev-sharma-bail-delhi-high-court-journalist-official-secrets-act-china%5C%22%3Egave%20him%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20trading%20in%20military%20secrets.%20His%20name%20was%20besmirched%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20since%20the%20police%20version%20was%20highlighted.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20a%20lot%20depends%20on%20the%20judiciary%20in%20defending%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights%2C%20more%20so%20when%20the%20State%20is%20on%20the%20rampage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruse%20of%20Chinese%20funds%20is%20a%20low%20trick%20that%20bears%20a%20closer%20look.%20The%20much-touted%20illegal%20money%2C%20which%20is%20being%20sedulously%20suggested%2C%20relies%20on%20a%202021%20case%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20against%20the%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20whose%20journalists%20have%20been%20raided%20and%20arrested.%20The%20ongoing%20case%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20journey%20without%20end%2C%20such%20are%20the%20gifts%20of%20the%20regime.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20so-called%20Chinese%20funding%20is%20an%20investment%20by%20a%20listed%20US%20company%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20business%20venture%20that%20is%20legally%20permissible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20investment%20then%20is%20far%20from%20being%20Chinese%2C%20although%20the%20US%20partner%20in%20question%20is%20said%20to%20be%20sympathetic%20to%20China.%20Even%20so%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20news%20and%20views%20coverage%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20suggest%20an%20underlying%20pro-China%20sentiment%20over%20the%20years%20%E2%80%93%20not%20that%20this%20can%20be%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20innuendo%20against%20this%20portal%20appears%20to%20rely%20wholly%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3Eshoddy%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20August%2C%20in%20which%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20mentioned%20in%20passing%20as%20an%20entity%20that%20%E2%80%9Csprinkles%E2%80%9D%20Chinese%20%E2%80%9Ctalking%20points%E2%80%9D.%20Typical%20innuendo%20of%20the%20long-dead%20Cold%20War%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20where%20is%20the%20proof%3F%20Have%20Indian%20investigators%20run%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20through%20a%20check%20and%20vet%20process%2C%20or%20have%20they%20conveniently%20adopted%20it%20wholesale%20in%20order%20to%20strike%20at%20a%20stream%20of%20journalism%20in%20India%20that%20appears%20to%20embarrass%20the%20regime%2C%20which%20has%20of%20late%20come%20to%20encounter%20serious%20political%20opposition%20in%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20half-decent%20judicial%20authority%20will%20easily%20see%20through%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20game.%20Given%20today%E2%80%99s%20political%20context%2C%20it%20would%20appear%20that%20other%20journalists%20who%20question%20and%20argue%20and%20refuse%20to%20kowtow%2C%20are%20now%20more%20likely%20to%20attract%20a%20greater%20degree%20of%20government%20ire%20than%20previously.%20Key%20state%20and%20national%20elections%20are%20approaching.%20The%20stakes%20are%20getting%20higher.%20The%20October%203%20development%20is%20a%20pointer.%20Spreading%20communal%20mayhem%2C%20and%20largesse%20for%20big%20capital%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20prove%20less%20easy%20now%20as%20people%20are%20getting%20wiser.%20For%20the%20regime%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20bad%20name%20and%20then%20shooting%20the%20messenger%20is%20the%20easy%20way%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20those%20picked%20up%20for%20questioning%20are%20employees%20of%20the%20news%20portal%20in%20question%20or%20contribute%20to%20it%20while%20being%20independent%20writers%20or%20video%20producers%2C%20and%20as%20such%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20acquainted%20with%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20financial%20dealings.%20So%2C%20why%20pick%20on%20them%20if%20not%20to%20spread%20anxiety%20in%20the%20media%3F%C2%A0%20Crucially%2C%20one%20of%20them%2C%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20is%20a%20leading%20international%20expositor%20of%20the%20games%20that%20the%20magnate%20Gautam%20Adani%20has%20played%20in%20his%20controversial%20financial%20and%20stock%20market%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20by%20now%20well%20understood%20that%20Adani%20enjoys%20a%20relationship%20of%20great%20mutual%20trust%20and%20warmth%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%20Guha%20Thakurta%20would%20have%20been%20given%20a%20piece%20of%20hell%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20police%20on%20account%20of%20the%20Adani%20factor%2C%20rather%20than%20anything%20else.%20Nobody%20can%20believe%20he%20is%20a%20propagandist%20for%20China%20or%20any%20other%20foreign%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.10-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.10-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.10-PM-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678406%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJournalist%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20who%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20speaks%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20October%204%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20the%20curious%20case%20of%20some%20non-journalists.%20Sanjay%20Rajoura%2C%20D.%20Raghunandan%2C%20and%20Sohail%20Hashmi.%20Rajoura%20is%20a%20famous%20stand-up%20comic%20who%20is%20known%20to%20take%20the%20mickey%20out%20of%20the%20regime%20The%20second%20named%20is%20a%20scientist%20and%20science%20propagator%2C%20and%20Hashmi%20is%20an%20amateur%20historian%20and%20cultural%20activist%20with%20a%20broad%20left-wing%20inclination.%20Why%20were%20they%20questioned%20and%20their%20laptops%20and%20mobile%20phones%20seized%3F%20On%20the%20whole%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20those%20picked%20up%20for%20questioning%2C%20or%20later%20arrested%2C%20have%20one%20common%20trait%3A%20they%20do%20not%20take%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20actions%2C%20and%20policies%20at%20face%20value%20%E2%80%93%20and%20question%20and%20propagate%20alternative%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20broad-brush%20terms%2C%20these%20may%20be%20narratives%20of%20the%20wider%20non-party%20Left%20in%20India%20concerned%20with%20the%20lives%20of%20ordinary%20people%2C%20the%20virtues%20of%20rationality%20and%20the%20methods%20of%20science%2C%20and%20the%20outright%20rejection%20of%20communalism%20or%20majoritarian%20thought%20in%20any%20form.%20In%20political%20terms%2C%20this%20section%20of%20opinion%20has%20grown%20in%20recent%20times%20as%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20have%20reneged%20on%20promise%20upon%20promise%20and%20converted%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20territory%20into%20a%20religious%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20Modi%20too%2C%20India%20was%20hardly%20the%20pristine%2C%20ideal%2C%20democracy%20in%20the%20poverty-stricken%2C%20sub-tropical%20regions%20of%20the%20world%2C%20as%20its%20makers%2C%20through%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20may%20have%20desired%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20Gandhi%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20on%20whom%20fell%20the%20burden%20to%20first%20lead%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndividual%20journalists%20were%20attacked%20by%20the%20State%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20In%20the%20Emergency%20years%2C%20journalists%20were%20jailed.%20Subsequently%20too%2C%20journalists%20were%20picked%20up%20on%20false%20charges%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Modi%20years.%20But%20the%20events%20of%20October%203%20are%20in%20a%20class%20of%20their%20own%20on%20account%20of%20the%20widespread%20extent%20of%20the%20single-day%20attack%2C%20which%20we%20cannot%20say%20for%20sure%20has%20ended.%20Renewed%20questioning%20or%20more%20arrests%20can%20hardly%20be%20ruled%20out.%20The%20message%20of%20intimidation%20continues%20to%20ring%20loudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20name%20of%20day-long%20interrogation%20has%20been%20recorded%2C%20in%20the%20public%20interest%2C%20by%20two%20prominent%20and%20outstanding%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-journos-questioned-delhi-riots-farmers-protest-covid-crisis%5C%22%3EAbhisar%20Sharma%20and%20Guha%20Thakurta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20they%20emerged%20from%20an%20ordeal%20that%20would%20have%20left%20anyone%20shaken.%20But%20these%20two%20remain%20steady%2C%20confident%20and%20unrepentant%2C%20ready%20to%20get%20on%20with%20their%20professional%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20the%20founder-editor%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20relatively%20small%20news%20and%20current%20affairs%20portal%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20but%20one%20with%20growing%20influence%20on%20account%20of%20its%20fact-based%20coverage%20that%20the%20regime%20does%20not%20like%2C%20and%20a%20senior%20manager%20of%20the%20portal%2C%20Amit%20Chakravarty%2C%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20apprehended%20under%20the%20dreaded%20UAPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fgyan-prakash-modi-govt-prabir-purkayastha%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Modi%20Govt%20May%20Say%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%2C%20But%20Is%20Turning%20India%20Into%20a%20Graveyard%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUAPA%20is%20rightly%20condemned%20as%20an%20unlawful%20law%20by%20political%20activists%20and%20legal%20luminaries%20alike%20because%2C%20as%20the%20provision%20now%20stands%2C%20the%20government%20can%20simply%20declare%20any%20individual%20of%20being%20a%20terrorist%20without%20furnishing%20evidence%20and%20going%20through%20even%20the%20motions%20of%20due%20process%2C%20put%20them%20in%20jail%2C%20and%20throw%20away%20the%20keys.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%202016-20%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fuapa-case-data-process-punishment-home-ministry-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3Esome%2024%2C000%20individuals%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20booked%20under%20UAPA%2C%20according%20to%20official%20figures.%20The%20conviction%20rate%20is%20a%20mere%202%25%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20cases%20are%20mostly%20bogus%2C%20if%20not%20downright%20fictitious.%20Thus%2C%20nearly%20all%20those%20taken%20in%20under%20UAPA%20are%20languishing%20in%20jail%20in%20miserable%20conditions%2C%20awaiting%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20the%20fate%20that%20awaits%20a%20prominent%20founder-editor%20whose%20organisation%20did%20some%20of%20the%20more%20meaningful%20reporting%20of%20the%20year-long%20movement%20against%20the%20egregious%20NRC-CAA%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20re-define%20the%20notion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20citizenship%20on%20a%20straightforward%20communal%20basis%20by%20a%20biased%20regime%3B%20and%20again%20the%20year-long%20movement%20of%20farmers%20against%20the%20now%20discredited%20farm%20laws%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20pushed%20by%20the%20regime%20to%20propitiate%20Big%20Capital%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20sobering%20to%20recall%20that%20a%20Jesuit%2C%20the%2080-year-old%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20a%20UAPA%20prisoner%20highly%20regarded%20for%20his%20selfless%20work%20amongst%20the%20poor%20tribal%20people%20of%20Jharkhand%20and%20for%20his%20ascetic%20way%20of%20life%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fstan-swamys-death-uapa-terrorism-bhim-koregaon-justice-undertrial%5C%22%3Edied%20in%20custody%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20denied%20any%20worthwhile%20medical%20assistance.%20Almost%20all%20those%20arrested%20along%20with%20Fr%20Swamy%20%E2%80%93%20among%20them%20scholars%2C%20intellectuals%20and%20academics%2C%20a%20revolutionary%20poet%20and%20bard%2C%20besides%20a%20journalist-activist%2C%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20infamous%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%20of%202018%2C%20are%20still%20facing%20the%20serious%20charge%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEspecially%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20made%20the%20right%20noises%20but%20can%20hardly%20be%20said%20to%20have%20covered%20itself%20with%20glory.%20In%20sensitive%20matters%2C%20when%20in%20a%20bind%2C%20the%20lower%20judiciary%20seems%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20anxiety%20and%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20by%20technicality%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20the%20meat%20of%20the%20matter%20a%20wide%20berth.%20This%2C%20at%20any%20rate%2C%20is%20the%20popular%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20polished%2C%20high-order%2C%20representation%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmedia-organisations-write-chandrachud-freedom-press%5C%22%3Eappeal%20was%20made%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20by%20the%20media%20fraternity%20on%20October%204%2C%20following%20the%20brazen%2C%20broad%20daylight%20repression%20of%20the%20media%20and%20after%20a%20powerful%20protest%20meeting%20of%20journalists%2C%20writers%20and%20prominent%20citizens%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20This%20could%20well%20be%20a%20weathervane%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalicious%20and%20mindless%20misuse%20of%20the%20UAPA%3F%20Journalists%20as%20terrorists%3F%20These%20are%20the%20points%20of%20consideration.%20In%20a%20democracy%2C%20must%20the%20privileges%2C%20rights%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20juridical%20persona%20of%20citizens%20be%20made%20automatically%20and%20naturally%20subservient%20to%20the%20whims%2C%20prejudices%20and%20malafide%20actions%20of%20the%20State%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12175442%2Fuapa.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22891%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12175442%2Fuapa.png%20891w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12175442%2Fuapa-300x167.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-509479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22497%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%20are%20appealed%20against%20before%20an%20appropriate%20court%2C%20will%20leaders%20of%20the%20judiciary%20stand%20by%20the%20citizen%20against%20the%20state%2C%20and%20strike%20down%20the%20more%20dangerous%20provisions%20of%20the%20UAPA%20or%20direct%20their%20modification%20so%20that%20ordinary%20citizens%20are%20not%20placed%20on%20the%20same%20footing%20as%20terrorists%3F%20Parliament%20makes%20laws%2C%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20interprets%20them%2C%20and%20interpretations%20constitute%20a%20part%20of%20the%20body%20of%20laws.%20We%20will%20know%20if%20the%20top%20court%20is%20ready%20to%20step%20up%20to%20the%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20succession%20of%20communal%20onslaughts%20against%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20principal%20religious%20minorities%20and%20the%20Untouchables%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EChaturvarnashram%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20the%20four-tier%20rigid%20caste%20hierarchy%20of%20traditional%2C%20un-reformed%2C%20Hindu%20social%20order%2C%20that%20have%20occurred%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20journalism%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20and%20its%20slow%20subversion%20and%20cooption%2C%20does%20appear%20to%20be%20the%20most%20defining%20and%20egregious%20feature%20of%20the%20New%20India%20being%20propagated%20and%20presided%20over%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20acolytes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Modi%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene%20in%202014%2C%20he%20made%20ritualistic%20noises%20about%20treating%20all%20citizens%20equally%20and%20was%2C%20oddly%20enough%2C%20believed%20by%20many.%20Truly%2C%20there%20was%20innocence%20abroad.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20PM%20gave%20the%20call%20for%20a%20Congress-%3Cem%3Emukt%3C%2Fem%3E%20Bharat%20%E2%80%93%20calling%20upon%20Indians%20to%20throw%20out%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20believing%20that%20the%20country%20was%20in%20love%20with%20him%20and%20had%20ejected%20his%20opponents%20from%20its%20affections%20and%20its%20consciousness.%20Other%20than%20that%2C%20a%20full-throttle%20attack%20on%20the%20opposition%20parties%20was%20still%20in%20the%20future.%20But%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20media%20was%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERight%20from%202014%2C%C2%A0%20the%20regime%2C%20its%20beneficiaries%2C%20its%20ideological%20subsidiaries%20and%20its%20dependents%2C%20have%20moved%20heaven%20and%20earth%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccapture%E2%80%9D%20the%20Indian%20media%2C%20using%20a%20variety%20of%20techniques%2C%20the%20carrot%20and%20the%20stick%20%E2%80%93%20even%20a%20buyout%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-ndtv-adani-ravish-kumar-karan-thapar%5C%22%3Eas%20the%20case%20of%20NDTV%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20express%20purpose%20of%20this%20extensive%20and%20expensive%20exercise%20lasting%20nearly%2010%20years%20was%20to%20rub%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20objective%20journalism%2C%20the%20testing%20of%20government%20and%20ruling%20party%20claims%2C%20out%20of%20the%20default%20mode%20in%20mainstream%20journalism%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20simultaneous%20objective%20was%20to%20acquire%20a%20long%20string%20of%20clapper%20boys%20through%20the%20media%20system%20who%20would%20sing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20praise%20%E2%80%93%20and%20taunt%20its%20opponents%20%E2%80%93%20from%20morning%20to%20night%20(although%20now%2C%20this%20makes%20people%20sick).%20This%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20worked%20as%20planned%2C%20and%20alternatives%20have%20mushroomed%20in%20the%20form%20of%20strong%20news%20portals%20and%20YouTube%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20regime%20seeking%20to%20perpetuate%20itself%2C%20marrying%20a%20majoritarian%20communal%20ideological%20agenda%20and%20its%20accompanying%20politics%20with%20Big%20Capital%20was%20crucial%2C%20but%20without%20full%20control%20over%20the%20media%20space%2C%20the%20enterprise%20would%20never%20be%20secure.%20After%20gaining%20control%20of%20mainline%20media%2C%20the%20newly%20sprung%20foci%20of%20rebellion%20too%20needed%20to%20be%20conquered.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20transpired%20on%20October%203.%20The%20propaganda%20cry%20of%20catching%20terrorists%20and%20Chinese%20agents%20is%20for%20the%20gullible.%20The%20real%20game%20is%20to%20bring%20opponents%20of%20any%20stripe%2C%20persuasion%2C%20or%20profession%2C%20to%20heel.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20trick%20has%20not%20worked.%20There%20has%20been%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20regime%E2%80%99s%20aim%20and%20plan%20may%20be%20to%20alter%20the%20basic%20character%20of%20the%20democratic%20state%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20how%20flawed%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20have%20inherited%2C%20but%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20hard%20to%20bring%20about%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20electoral%20politics%20alone.%20Resistance%20is%20scattered%20through%20the%20country%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20pockets%20and%20islands%2C%20but%20no%20less%20importantly%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20arguments%2C%20languages%2C%20and%20belief%20systems%20of%20the%20people.%20Karnataka%20the%20past%20May%20was%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20vast%20and%20varied%20land%20with%20multiple%20histories%20and%20geographies%2C%20people%20seek%20mutual%20engagement%2C%20stability%20and%20harmony%20%E2%80%93%20and%20not%20sameness%20and%20uniformity.%20The%20Third%20Reich%20is%20unlikely%20to%20follow%20the%20German%20route%20here%20and%20come%20on%20the%20back%20of%20elections%2C%20even%20rigged%20ones.%20More%20dire%20means%20would%20need%20to%20be%20devised.%20One%20way%20or%20another%2C%20there%20is%20much%20to%20do%20for%20a%20media%20that%20wishes%20to%20keep%20encroachers%20at%20bay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696494550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134247%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.11-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthrottling-what-remains-of-independent-media-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20propaganda%20cry%20of%20catching%20terrorists%20and%20Chi