mber%20of%20women%20promoted%20inched%20up%20from%2086%20in%202021%2C%20but%20they're%20still%20getting%20overlooked%20despite%20asking%20for%20promotions%20at%20the%20same%20rate%20as%20men%2C%20the%20survey%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20for%20the%20gap%3A%20the%20way%20men%20and%20women%20tend%20to%20receive%20their%20promotions.%20%26quot%3BWe%20promote%20men%20based%20on%20potential%20and%20women%20have%20to%20have%20already%20proven%20it%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandberg%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20prove%20you%20can%20be%20a%20manager%20until%20you're%20a%20manager.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20are%20even%20worse%20for%20Black%20women%2C%20who%20are%20being%20promoted%20at%20the%20lowest%20rate%20in%20at%20least%20five%20years%20compared%20with%20men.%20Only%2054%20Black%20women%20were%20promoted%20last%20year%20for%20every%20100%20men%2C%20down%20from%2096%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20which%20started%20tracking%20respondents'%20race%20in%202018.%20The%20number%20is%20now%20closer%20to%20the%2058%20seen%20in%202018%20and%202019%2C%20before%20the%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%20protests%20prompted%20much%20of%20corporate%20America%20to%20promise%20to%20hire%20more%20people%20of%20color.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20based%20on%20research%20from%20276%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20and%20including%20a%20survey%20of%20more%20than%2027%2C000%20employees%20from%2033%20firms%2C%20found%20that%20men%20also%20benefited%20disproportionately%20from%20in-office%20work%20compared%20with%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMen%20report%20when%20they%20are%20on-site%20that%20they%20get%20more%20mentorship%20and%20sponsorship%20than%20women.%20They%20feel%20more%20'in%20the%20know%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Rachel%20Thomas%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20LeanIn.Org.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20that's%20already%20happening%20when%20everyone's%20in%20the%20office%2C%20the%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20on%20an%20even%20broader%20scale%20in%20a%20hybrid%20work%20environment.%20Thomas%20suggested%20companies%20need%20to%20better%20train%20managers%20to%20evaluate%20workers%20on%20flexible%20schedules%2C%20and%20that%20performance%20reviews%20need%20to%20be%20redesigned%20to%20emphasize%20results%2C%20not%20when%20and%20where%20work%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20perception%20that%20it's%20women%20who%20are%20lazy%2C%20who%20are%20disgruntled%2C%20that%20it's%20women%20who%20are%20demanding%20flexibility%20rather%20than%20how%20that%20flexibility%20can%20fuel%20ambition%20is%20really%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sandberg%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20Meta%20Platforms%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20found%20that%20women%20are%20more%20ambitious%20than%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20with%20about%2080%25%20saying%20they'd%20like%20a%20promotion%20compared%20with%2070%25%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E--%20With%20assistance%20from%20Kelsey%20Butler.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696494480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fesdtcg6_gender-pay-gap_625x300_20_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmore-men-getting-promotions-at-work-than-women-report-explains-why-4452097%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20want%20to%20be%20leaders%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20but%20employers%20are%20still%20passing%20them%20by%20in%20favor%20of%20their%20male%20counterparts.For%20every%20100%20men%20promoted%20to%20a%20manager%20role%20in%202022%2C%20only%2087%20women%20received%20the%20same%20boost.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwor