%20India%20Can%20Win%20100%20Medals%2C%20Fulfil%3B%20'Sau%20Paar'%20Prophecy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20contingent%20recorded%20its%20biggest-ever%20medal%20haul%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Asian%20Games%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20as%20it%20went%20past%20the%2070%20mark%20at%20the%20Hangzhou%20event.%20As%20the%20sporting%20world%20lauded%20the%20Indian%20athletes%20in%20China%20for%20their%20stupendous%20effort%2C%20many%20reminded%20them%20that%20the%20job%20wasn't%20yet%20done.%20The%20target%20for%20the%20Indian%20contingent%20has%20been%20going%20past%20the%20100-medal%20mark%20in%20the%202022%20Asian%20Games%2C%20and%20with%20four%20days%20to%20go%20before%20the%20event%20concludes%2C%20there's%20every%20possibility%20of%20that%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20already%20won%2083%20medals%2C%20including%20the%20archery%20women's%20team%20gold%20medal%20and%20mixed%20doubles%20squash%20gold%20that%20came%20on%20Thursday%2C%20India%20need%2017%20more%20medals%20to%20touch%20the%20100-medal%20mark.%20If%20things%20go%20as%20planned%20over%20the%20remaining%20days%2C%20the%20overall%20medals%20tally%20would%20go%20past%20the%20century%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20India%20can%20go%20past%20the%20100-medal%20mark%20in%20Hangzhou%20Asian%20Games%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESquash%3A%201%20Medal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20mixed%20doubles%20event%20after%20Dipika%20Pallikal%20and%20Harinder%20Pal%20Singh%20Sandhu%20defeated%20the%20Malaysian%20pair.%20India%20are%20assured%20of%20another%20medal%20in%20squash%2C%20having%20reached%20the%20men's%20singles%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWrestling%3A%206%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFreestyle%20wrestling%20is%20where%20India%20are%20at%20their%20strongest%20in%20the%20sport.%20With%20Antim%20Panghal%2C%20Pooja%20Gehlot%20participating%2C%20India%20can%20hope%20for%202%20medals%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20also%20have%20Kiran%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20participating%20in%20the%2065kg%20and%2076kg%20categories%20respectively%2C%20India%20can%20expect%20medals%20from%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Punia%20and%20Sumit%20also%20remain%20two%20top%20contenders%20in%20the%20men's%20freestyle%2086kg%20and%20125kg%20categories%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHockey%3A%202%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20men's%20team%20has%20entered%20the%20final%20and%20is%20assured%20of%20a%20medal.%C2%A0The%20women's%20team%20is%20also%20in%20the%20semi-finals%2C%20without%20losing%20a%20single%20contest.%20The%20side%20is%20expected%20to%20fetch%20at%20least%20a%20medal.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20colour%20of%20those%20medals%20will%20be%20golden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchery%3A%203%20medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20compound%20events%2C%20India%20have%20been%20a%20formidable%20force%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20Jyothi%20Surekha%20is%20expected%20to%20fetch%20India%20a%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20individual%20final.%20Having%20reached%20the%20final%2C%20she%20is%20already%20assured%20of%20a%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20men's%20compound%20gold%20medal%20match%2C%20India%20are%20assured%20of%20two%20medals%2C%20with%20Abhishek%20Verma%20and%20Ojas%20Pravin%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECricket%3A%201%20Medal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Indian%20women's%20cricket%20team%20already%20fetching%20gold%2C%20nothing%20less%20than%20another%20yellow%20metal%20is%20expected%20from%20the%20men's%20cricket%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKabaddi%3A%202%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20both%20in%20men's%20and%20women's%20categories%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20return%20with%20gold%20medals%20from%20kabaddi.%20While%20bagging%20the%20top%20podium%20spot%20isn't%20a%20certainty%2C%20two%20medals%20are%20quite%20likely%20from%20the%20two%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBadminton%3A%202%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHS%20Prannoy%20made%20it%20to%20the%20semi-finals%20in%20the%20men's%20singles%20category%2C%20assuring%20India%20of%20at%20least%20a%20bronze%20in%20the%20event.%20The%20mens'%20doubles%20pair%20of%20Chirag%20Shetty%20and%20Satwiksairaj%20Rankireddy%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20fetch%20India%20a%20medal%20in%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBridge%3A%201%20Medal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20qualified%20for%20the%20final%20against%20China%20in%20men's%20team%20event%2C%20assuring%20of%20at%20least%20a%20silver%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696488480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Frrssa898_neeraj-chopra-afp_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-how-india-can-go-past-100-medal-mark-fulfil-sau-ke-paar-prophecy-4451655%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20end%20of%20play%20on%20October%204%2C%20India%20had%20clinched%20a%20total%20of%2081%20medals%20in%20Hangzhou%20Asian%20Games.%20The%20target%20remains%20to%20reach%20the%20100-medal%20mark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-how-india-can-go-past-100-medal-mark-fulfil-sau-ke-paar-prophecy-4451655%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-how-india-can-go-past-100-medal-mark-fulfil-sau-ke-paar-prophecy-4451655%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasian-games-2023%2Fasian-games-how-india-can-go-past-100-medal-mark-fulfil-sau-ke-paar-prophecy-4451655%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nikki%20Haley%20overtakes%20Ron%20DeSantis%2C%20moves%20to%202nd%20place%20in%20New%20Hampshire%3A%20Poll%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696488393000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt