%20The%20site%20also%20revealed%20that%20Mike%20has%20worked%20to%20build%20up%20a%20%26quot%3Btolerance%20to%20spiciness%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWatch%20the%20video%20of%20Mike%20setting%20the%20record%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENew%20record%3A%20Fastest%20time%20to%20eat%2050%20carolina%20reaper%20chilli%20peppers%20-%206%20minutes%20and%2049.20%20seconds%20by%20Mike%20Jack%20%F0%9F%87%A8%F0%9F%87%A6%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20He%20eventually%20went%20on%20to%20eat%20135%20peppers%20in%20this%20one%20sitting%20%F0%9F%A4%AF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fb5OxTBtbjd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fb5OxTBtbjd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%23GWR2024%20OUT%20NOW%20(%40GWR)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGWR%2Fstatus%2F1706615782761799881%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EMike%20also%20holds%20the%20world%20record%20for%20the%20fastest%20time%20to%20drink%20a%20bottle%20of%20hot%20sauce%20(8.56%20seconds)%20and%20the%20fastest%20time%20to%20drink%20one%20litre%20of%20tomato%20sauce%20(1%20minute%205.56%20seconds)%20-%20both%20of%20which%20he%20achieved%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20a%20speed-eating%20world%20record%20for%20pasta%20made%20headlines%20across%20the%20globe.%20Leah%20Shutkever%2C%20a%20serial%20GWR%20title%20holder%2C%20became%20the%20quickest%20person%20to%20eat%20a%20bowl%20of%20pasta.%20There's%20also%20a%20video%20documenting%20her%20achievement.%20To%20know%20more%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Fwatch-woman-devours-pasta-to-set-world-record-guess-her-speed-4431899%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%3A%20Man%20Explains%20How%20To%20Eat%20Burger%20In%20Formal%20Settings%2C%20In