ya%20revealed%20that%20his%20character%20is%20a%20casanova%20but%20he%20wouldn't%20call%20himself%20that.%20He%20expressed%20his%20excitement%20about%20being%20part%20of%20the%20Zoya%20Akhtar%20directorial%2C%20which%20will%20be%20streamed%20in%20190%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Male%20Nanny%20Sentenced%20For%20690%20Years%20For%20Molesting%2016%20Boys%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2034-year-old%20male%20nanny%20is%20facing%20a%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20690%20years%20to%20life.%20He%20has%20been%20found%20guilty%20of%20molesting%2016%20boys%20and%20showing%20another%20boy%20pornography%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Forangecountyda.org%2Fpress%2Fmale-nanny-convicted-of-molesting-16-young-boys-under-his-care-and-showing-pornography-to-a-17th-boy-victims-ranged-from-2-to-12-years-old-34-year-old-costa-mesa-man-faces-a-maximum-sentence-of-690-y%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOrange%20County%20District%20Attorney's%20Office%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Zakrzewski%20of%20Costa%20Mesa%20has%20been%20convicted%20by%20a%20jury%20of%2034%20felonies%2C%20including%2027%20felony%20counts%20of%20lewd%20and%20lascivious%20acts%20with%20a%20minor%20under%20the%20age%20of%2014%2C%20two%20felony%20counts%20of%20oral%20copulation%20of%20a%20child%20under%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20and%20one%20felony%20count%20of%20possession%20of%20child%20pornography.%20He%20also%20faces%20one%20felony%20count%20of%20using%20a%20minor%20for%20sex%20acts%2C%20two%20felony%20counts%20of%20distributing%20pornography%20to%20a%20minor%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20conduct%2C%20and%20one%20felony%20count%20of%20an%20attempted%20lewd%20or%20lascivious%20act%20with%20a%20minor%20under%20the%20age%20of%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20convicted%20Zakrzewski%20of%20all%2034%20felonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%