Buddy%20Program%2C'%26quot%3B%20Zakrzewski%20stated%20on%20the%20Sitter%20Buddy%20website.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20am%20a%20full-service%20TrustLine%20Certified%20provider%20of%20regular%20and%20on-demand%20childcare%2C%20as%20well%20as%20mentoring%20services%20for%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20committed%20these%20crimes%20between%20January%201%2C%202014%20and%20May%2017%2C%202019.%20He%20faces%20690%20years%20to%20life%20plus%20eight%20years%20when%20he%20is%20sentenced%20on%20November%2017%2C%202023%2C%20at%20the%20Central%20Justice%20Center%20in%20Santa%20Ana%20in%20Department%20C30.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20in%20May%202019%20when%20a%20Laguna%20Beach%20couple%20reported%20to%20the%20police%20that%20their%20babysitter%2C%20Zakrzewski%2C%20had%20touched%20their%20eight-year-old%20son%20inappropriately%20and%20was%20concerned%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20son%20and%20potentially%20other%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20immediately%20opened%20an%20investigation%2C%20which%20led%20to%3Cbr%3E%20the%20identification%20of%20a%20second%20seven-year-old%20victim%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20ten%20more%20boys%20from%20across%20Southern%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696485780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fj9rl6ipg_matthew-zakrzewski_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-sentenced-for-690-years-for-molesting-16-boys-in-us-4451620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Matthew%20Zakrzewski%20served%20as%20a%20male%20nanny%20for%20families%20across%20Southern%20California%20and%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20original%20Sitter%20Buddy%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmale-nanny-sentenced-for-690-years-for-molesting-16-boys-in-us-4451620%22%2C%22cdnAmpU