of%20herald%20of%20their%20ascendancy%20in%20international%20cricket%2C%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20was%20a%20herald%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20discovery%20of%20the%20One%20Day%20International%20and%20their%20emergence%20as%20a%20world%20power.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20had%20great%20significance%2C%20as%20a%20coronation%20ceremony%20for%20powerful%20teams.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20ways%20even%20though%20the%20bilateral%20ODI%20as%20a%20format%20is%20in%20decline%2C%20the%20World%20Cup%20still%20has%20cut%20through.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20cricket%20world%20has%20to%20stop%20and%20the%20cricket%20world%20very%20seldom%20stops%20these%20days%20for%20anything%20but%20premium%20events%20such%20as%20the%20IPL.%20So%20yeah%2C%20I%20think%20you%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20read%20into%20the%20surrounding%20malaise%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20or%20any%20sort%20of%20decline%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%E2%80%99s%20appeal.%20In%20some%20respects%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20simply%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20just%20so%20much%20cricket%20nowadays%20and%20that%20teams%20very%20very%20seldom%20play%20their%20full-strength%2011s.%20They%E2%80%99re%20often%20resting%20players%2C%20players%20are%20missing%20out%20through%20injury%20or%20they%E2%80%99re%20being%20saved%20for%20more%20important%20series%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20saving%20themselves%20to%20play%20International%20T20.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20players%20will%20be%20available%2C%20the%20best%2011s%2C%20for%20this%20World%20Cup%2C%20even%20though%20there%20may%20be%20some%20uncertainty%20about%20those%20best%2011s%20because%20certain%20individual%20players%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20enough%20recent%20game%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Speaking%20of%20game%20time%2C%20I%20was%20just%20checking%20odds%2C%20which%20I%20normally%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Before%20world%20cups%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20you%20look%20and%20see%20okay%20who%E2%80%99s%20the%20favourite%3F%20What%20is%20the%20betting%20world%20saying%3F%20The%20sequence%20is%20quite%20simply%3A%20India%20favourites%2C%20England%20second%2C%20Australia%20third%2C%20Pakistan%20fourth%20and%20so%20on.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20ask%20you%20about%20Australia.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20played%20very%20few%20One%20Day%20Internationals%20this%20year.%20When%20they%20came%20into%20this%20One%20Day%20tournament%2C%20they%20played%20the%20white%20ball%20series%20against%20India%20recently%20when%20they%20had%20come%3B%20they%20just%20played%20nine.%20They%20played%20the%20fewest%20amongst%20all%20the%20countries.%20So%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20there%3F%20I%20mean%20I%20know%20there%20are%20injuries%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20hearing%20all%20kinds%20of%20stories.%20They%20had%20a%20good%20game%20the%20other%20day%20but%20it%20was%20against%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20which%20is%20a%20considerably%20weaker%20team.%20What%E2%80%99s%20the%20buzz%20like%20in%20Australia%3F%20What%20are%20people%20saying%3F%20What%20does%20it%20look%20like%3F%20Australia%20is%20the%20biggest%20World%20Cup%20nation%20in%20cricket%2C%20with%20five%20wins!%20Boring%2C%20but%20yeah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yeah%2C%20well%20of%20course%2C%20we%20had%20an%20ODI%20series%20cancelled%20in%20South%20Africa%20earlier%20this%20year%20because%20the%20South%20African%20Board%20wanted%20its%20players%20to%20be%20available%20for%20its%20new%20domestic%20T20.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20as%20much%20as%20we%E2%80%99d%20planned%20on%20having.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20an%20Ashes%20series%20this%20year%20for%20which%20players%20have%20been%20protected.%20You%20know%2C%20to%20us%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%2C%20very%20important%20how%20we%20do%20in%20the%20Ashes.%20Every%20Ashes%20year%2C%20everything%20else%20falls%20into%20secondary%20importance.%20I%20think%20we%E2%80%99ve%20got%20a%20vague%20idea%20about%20our%20best%2011%2C