20disappearance%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20on%20an%20ocean%20liner%20in%201949%2C%20the%20story%20of%20which%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20last%20year.%20I%20found%20it%20very%20fascinating.%20I%20was%20intensely%20curious%20about%20it%20and%20of%20course%2C%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20you%20go%2C%20%E2%80%98Well%2C%20the%20only%20way%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20find%20out%20more%20about%20this%20is%20if%20I%20write%20a%20book.%E2%80%99%20So%20that%20tends%20to%20be%20what%20I%20do.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20niche%20publication.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20published%20myself%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20for%20sale%20from%20my%20kitchen%20table%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20fun.%20It%E2%80%99s%20seriously%20interesting.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20period%20in%20Australian%20history%20that%20I%20find%20very%2C%20very%20fascinating%3B%2010%20years%20after%20the%20World%20War%20II%20and%20before%20the%20advent%20of%20television%20when%20a%20lot%20was%20happening%20in%20Australia.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20doing%20things%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20a%20busy%20society.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20as%20conservative%20and%20stale%20as%20we%20sometimes%20think%20and%20outlandish%20things%20happened.%20A%20young%20woman%20disappearing%20on%20an%20ocean%20liner%20indicates%20that%20the%20world%20that%20she%20inhabited%20and%20the%20people%20that%20she%20fraternised%20with%20and%20the%20society%20of%20which%20she%20was%20part%2C%20is%20intensely%20interesting.%20Like%20all%20crimes%2C%20like%20all%20terrible%20mishaps%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20aperture%20through%20which%20to%20study%20the%20relevant%20society.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20what%20really%20interests%20me%20about%20these%20things.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20particularly%20drawn%20to%20violence%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20particularly%20drawn%20to%20scandal%20but%20I%20am%20interested%20in%20social%20relations%20and%20the%20shape%20of%2