%20saving%20cricket%20from%20itself.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20hard%20to%20take%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20a%20good%20team%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20great%20players%20in%20them.%20They%E2%80%99re%20very%20good%20to%20watch.%20I%20just%20wish%20as%20I%20wrote%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20series%2C%20that%20England%20didn%E2%80%99t%20behave%20like%20they%20expected%20a%20standing%20ovation%20every%20time%20they%20walked%20into%20the%20room.%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20great%20the%20way%20you%20think%20it%20brings%20us%20all%20together%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Seriously!%20So%2C%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20listening%20to%20this.%20I%20mean%20they%20are%20a%20phenomenally%20awesome%20team%20and%20their%20batting%20is%20terrific%20and%20their%20bowling%20is%20terrific.%20Anyhow%20we%E2%80%99ll%20see%20how%20that%20goes%20but%20you%20do%20know%20that%20they%20are%20playing%20them%20in%20Lucknow.%20India%20is%20playing%20England%20in%20Lucknow%20which%20is%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%2C%20the%20Wicket%20has%20been%20relayed.%20It%20got%20very%20bad%20marks%20during%20the%20IPL%20and%20the%20highest%20total%20on%20that%20ground%20is%2C%20I%20think%2C%20140.%20It%20could%20be%20off%20by%20five%20runs%2C%20this%20way%20or%20that%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20They%E2%80%99re%20my%20favourite%20games%20though.%20150%20versus%20160%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20the%20best.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20see%20100%20versus%20300.%20You%20want%20everyone%20to%20count!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20So%2C%20the%20game%20is%20going%20to%20be%20played%20at%20Lucknow%20and%20I%20have%20a%20great%20story%20to%20tell%20you%20about%20Lucknow.%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20one%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20Santosh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20journalist%20there%20and%20he%20was%20telling%20me%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20when%20he