%3EThe%20proposal%20would%20have%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20UK%20parliament%2C%20with%20Sunak%20saying%20it%20will%20be%20a%20free%20vote%2C%20asking%20politicians%20to%20make%20their%20decision%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20matter%20of%20conscience.%26quot%3B%20Sunak%20added%20that%20smoking%20puts%20pressure%20on%20the%20NHS%2C%20with%20costs%20of%20%C2%A317%20billion%20(%2420.7%20billion)%20a%20year%2C%20and%20the%20move%20would%20help%20the%20UK%20toward%20its%20goal%20to%20become%20smoke-free%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Imperial%20Brands%20Plc%2C%20the%20biggest%20seller%20of%20cigarettes%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20fell%20as%20much%20as%204.3%25%20in%20London.%20British%20American%20Tobacco%20Plc%2C%20which%20gets%20most%20of%20its%20sales%20from%20markets%20outside%20Britain%2C%20was%20down%201.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20measure%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20aggressive%20anti-smoking%20policies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20though%20the%20UK%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first.%20New%20Zealand%20last%20year%20passed%20a%20law%20prohibiting%20the%20sale%20of%20cigarettes%20to%20anyone%20born%20after%202008.%20The%20current%20legal%20age%20to%20buy%20cigarettes%20in%20the%20UK%20is%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETobacco%20companies%20are%20racing%20to%20offer%20alternatives%2C%20such%20as%20vapes%2C%20devices%20that%20heat%20tobacco%20and%20oral%20nicotine.%20Sunak%20said%20the%20UK%20must%20%26quot%3Bact%20before%20vaping%20becomes%20endemic%2C%26quot%3B%20given%20that%20one%20in%20five%20children%20have%20used%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proposal%20to%20ban%20the%20legal%20sale%20of%20cigarettes%20over%20time%20threatens%20significant%20unintended%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20Imperial%20Brands%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Bloomberg.%20%26quot%3BOn%20vaping%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20government%20to%20create%20effective%20policies%20which%20prevent%20youth%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBr