%20the%20shade%20of%20a%20decades-old%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20tree%20in%20Hatmulla%20village.%20While%20in%20repose%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20this%20tree%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20surviving%20ones%20in%20the%20village%2C%20once%20known%20for%20its%20mighty%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20trees.%20So%20he%20decided%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20its%20dwindling%20plantation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocally%20called%20%3Cem%3Ebou%E2%80%99in%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Eboueen%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Kashmiri%20language%2C%20and%20scientifically%20known%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3EPlatanus%20orientalis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20tree%20grows%20over%2020%20metres%20in%20height%2C%20while%20its%20girth%20can%20go%20up%20to%2050%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chinar%20tree%20is%20highly%20revered%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294161%2Fkashmiri-farmer-haji-mohammad-shafi-sheikh-grows-exotic-pears%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKashmiri%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20natural%20heritage.%20The%20tree%20is%20frequently%20portrayed%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20artistic%2C%20poetic%2C%20and%20literary%20works.%20The%20oldest%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20tree%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20over%20700%20years%20old%20and%20is%20in%20Budgam%E2%80%99s%20Chattergam%20village%20with%20a%20girth%20of%20over%2050%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECome%202023%2C%20Khan%20has%20planted%20more%20than%20300%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hatmulla%2C%20which%20is%20adjacent%20to%20his%20native%20village%2C%20Nagri%20Malpora.%20Simultaneously%2C%20he%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20state%20forest%20department%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20of%20planting%20over%201%2C000%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Kupwara.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20now%20been%2015%20years%20since%20I%20planted%20%3Cem%3