%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.00-1695822990-500x224.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.00-1695822990-768x345.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.00-1695822990-1536x689.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-26-at-15.48.00-1695822990-150x67.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331080%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERamji%20has%20created%20a%20wall%20musuem%20tracing%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20history%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202018%2C%20and%20an%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20rocket%20model%2C%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Ramji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20once%20made%20a%20brass%20model%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EISRO%20rocket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Capacity%20Building%20and%20Public%20Outreach%20(CBPO)%20team%20at%20the%20ISRO%20headquarters%20were%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20model%20and%20called%20me%20for%20a%20meeting.%20They%20wanted%20me%20to%20build%20more%20rocket%20models%20for%20them.%20This%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20my%20dream%20turning%20into%20a%20reality%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2074%2C%20Ramji%20set%20up%20a%20space%20at%20his%20friend%20Moiz%20Vagh%E2%80%99s%20factory%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20backwards%20since%20then.%20The%20first%20order%20for%20%E2%80%98Craftizan%20Engineering%20models%E2%80%99%20was%20from%20ISRO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20designed%20models%20for%20%E2%80%98ISRO%20on%20wheels%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20were%20six%20buses%20filled%20with%20the%20space%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20satellites%20and%20rockets.%20We%20have%20had%20fantastic%20support%20from%20ISRO%20and%20have%20built%20various%20models%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ramji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%2C%20since%20then%2C%20placed%20thousands%20of%20orders%20for%20rocket%20models%20and%20kits.%20Craftizan%20Engineering%20also%20makes%201%3A2%20scale%20models%20with%20models%2050-75%20feet%20tall.%20Ramji%20has%20made%20models%20of%20all%20of%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20missions%20from%20Chandrayaan-1%2C%202%2C%203%20to%20Gaganyaan.%20Apart%20from%20ISRO%2C%20they%20design%20rockets%20for%20universities%2C%20schools%20and%20private%20dealers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20crafting%20at%20his%20home%2C%20he%20now%20has%20a%20team%20of%2050%20people%2C%20including%20designers%20and%20engineers.%20They%20also%20design%20train%20models%20and%20have%20showcased%20them%20at%20the%20Mysuru%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20built%20a%20wall%20museum%20which%20traces%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323066%2Fchandrayaan-3-the-history-of-how-india-began-one-of-its-most-significant-space-journeys%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EISRO%E2%80%99s%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20some%20private%20universities%20have%20placed%20orders%20for%20this%2C%20we%20want%20it%20to%20be%20placed%20at%20government%20schools.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%20is%20in%20talks%20to%20place%20these%20wall%20museums%20at%20many%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2079-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20currently%20working%20on%20wall%20museums%20at%20Science%20City%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20PSG%20college%20of%20engineering%2C%20Coimbatore%20and%20Savitha%20University%2C%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunities%20and%20more%20than%20enough%20work%20today.%20We%20have%20orders%20worth%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20per%20month%20and%20have%20plans%20of%20expanding.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Make%20in%20India%20push%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20go%20big%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Forget%20your%20age%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miniature%20models%20made%20by%20Craftizan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331084%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMiniature%20models%20made%20by%20Craftizan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20incredible%20to%20see%20how%20Ramji%20has%20the%20energy%20of%20a%2030-year-old.%20He%E2%80%99s%20raring%20to%20go%20and%20is%20looking%20at%20a%20world%20of%20opportunities.%20He%E2%80%99s%20got%20no%20plans%20of%20retiring%20any%20time%20soon.%20His%20day%20at%20the%20factory%20starts%20at%209%20am%20and%20goes%20on%20till%207-8pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20love%20to%20work%20on%20my%20models%20with%20some%20Carnatic%20music%20playing%20in%20the%20background.%20Age%20is%20never%20on%20my%20mind%20and%20I%20would%20love%20to%20work%20all%20365%20days.%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20that%20I%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20fulfil%20my%20passion.%20Everyday%20is%20a%20new%20job%20as%20we%20create%20something%20new%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20grateful%20that%20the%20opportunity%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20half%20a%20decade%20ago%20is%20available%20today.%20%E2%80%9CModel%20making%20is%20commercially%20viable%20today.%20As%20Chinese%20goods%20are%20banned%2C%20we%20are%20also%20looking%20at%20making%20metal%20moulds%20to%20make%20parts%20for%20toys%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20he%20satisfied%20with%20the%20work%20he%E2%80%99s%20done%3F%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20only%20scratched%20the%20surface%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replies.%20He%20would%20really%20like%20it%20if%20more%20children%20would%20take%20an%20interest%20in%20this%20field.%20He%20also%20tells%20how%20many%20engineering%20college%20students%20from%20Mysuru%20have%20visited%20Ramji%E2%80%99s%20factory%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20only%20done%2010%20percent%20of%20the%20work%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20do%20so%20far.%20Ninety%20percent%20of%20it%20is%20left.%20I%20want%20to%20propagate%20engineering%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20Children%20tend%20to%20pick%20up%20things%20early.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20Meccano%20like%20sets%20or%20kits%20to%20spur%20this%20interest.%20This%20teaches%20them%20basic%2C%20fundamental%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengineering%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20hope